Eyaka Natan Daudi olkilikuai

(
1   Int 
17  .
1  -
15  )


1  Ore apa ebikito olaiguanani te nkaji enye, neishoo ninye Olaitoriani enkiyeng'iyeng too lmang'ati lenyena pooki oomanita, 
2  nejoki olaiguanani Natan ilo oiboni, “Ng'ura taata, abikito nanu te nkaji oo ltarakua, kake ore osanduku le Nkai netonita ti atua olng'obor.” 
3  Nejoki Natan olaiguanani, “Shomo, taasa ina pooki natii atua oltau lino; amu etii Olaitoriani te nebo iyie.”


4  Kake ore ina kewarie ake nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enetii Natan ajoki, 
5  “Shomo tiaaki osinka lai Daudi, ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani: Amaa, eikishetaki iyie enkaji nabikie atua? 
6  Eitu ae kata nanu aton ti atua enkaji ebaiki enkolong apa nailepunye iltung'ana loo Siraeli aitung'uaa Misiri o metabaiki ena olong, kake to lng'obor oshi aloolo aitaa emanyisho ai. 
7  Ore ti atua iwuejitin pooki nashomo nanu te nebo iltung'ana pooki le Israel, eitu nanu airo ororei te likae hoo obo loo larishak loo Israeli laa ninche aitanapa meirrita iltung'ana laainei Israeli, ajoki “Kainyoo pee eitu kishetakiki nanu enkaji oo ltarakua?” ’ 
8  Ore naa nji tiaaki osinka lai Daudi, ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani loo lororani, aawa apa nanu iyie aitung'uaa enkirritare, aitung'uaa esujata oo nkerra, pee itum ataa olkitok te shumata iltung'ana laainei Israel; 
9  natii nanu te nebo iyie te pooki wueji nishomo, naar ilmang'ati linono pooki aiwuang'ie te dukuya ino; naa kaaitobiraki nanu iyie enkarna kitok, anaa enkarna e lelo kituaak le nkop. 
10  Naa kagelu nanu ewueji te nkaraki iltung'ana laainei Israel, naun nanu ninche, pee etum aatobik te wueji enye maate, nemeitokini ae kata aaitanyamal; nemeitoki iltung'ana lo larrabal aaisilisil ninche, anaa apa, 
11  ebaiki ina kata apa nagelu ilarishak apik shumata iltung'ana laainei Israel; naa kaaisho nanu iyie enkiyeng'iyeng too lmang'ati linono pooki. Ore ake eibalunye Olaitoriani te iyie nchere, eikintaa iyie Olaitoriani enkaji. 
12   Ore te neiputayu nkolong'i inono nirrag iyie te nebo loo papaai lino, nadamu nanu eishoi ino te siadi iyie, ilo olotu aing'uaa osesen lino, naitubulaa nanu enkitoo enye. 
13  Keshet ninye enkaji te nkaraki enkarna ai, naa kaitasheyie nanu olorika le nkitoo enye ntarasi. 
14   Naaku nanu papaai lenye, neaku ninye olayioni lai. Te neas ninye entorroni, naitame nanu ninye te ng'udi e tung'ana, o too oshot e tung'ana; 
15  kake maiwuang'ie nanu enyorrata ai nauno aitung'uaa ninye, anaa apa enaiwuang'ie te Saul, ilo apa laiwuang'ie nanu te dukuya iyie. 
16   Ore enkaji ino o enkitoria naa keitisipi te dukuya nanu; ore olorika lino le nkitoo keitasheyieki ntarasi.’ ” 
17  Ore te risioroto e kulo rorei, o te risioroto ena duata pooki, neirorie Natan Daudi.

Enkomono enkishooroto enashe e Daudi

(
1   Int 
17  .
16  -
27  )


18  Nelo olaiguanani Daudi atua neton te dukuya Olaitoriani, nejo, “Kara nanu ng'ae, Ee Olaitoriani Enkai, naa kainyoo enkaji ai, metaa eikiyaua nanu eneba nji? 
19  Ore ake eyia naa entoki kiti apa ena too nkonyek inono, Olaitoriani Enkai; iroro sii iyie te nkaraki enkaji o sinka lino te nkata sapuk nalotu, nikintoduaa nanu iishoritin naapuonu, Olaitoriani Enkai! 
20  Naa kainyoo epon Daudi pee kijoki iyie? Amu iyiolo iyie osinka lino, Olaitoriani Enkai! 
21  Te nkaraki enkisiligata ino, naa te risioroto oltau lino, itaasa iyie ena enkitoo aidimie osinka lino metayiolo ina. 
22  Metaa ira iyie kitok, Ee Olaitoriani Enkai; amu metii likae oikununo anaa iyie, nemetii ae Ai neme iyie ake, te risioroto e nena pooki nikitoning'o too nkiyiaa ang. 
23   Kalo likae orere ti oriong e nkop oikununo anaa iltung'ana linono Israel, laa ninche eshomo Enkai akordu aitaa iltung'ana lenyena, aitobiraki kewan enkarna, neas te nkaraki ninche intokitin kituaak naaitureisho, te araroto te dukuya iltung'ana lenyena iloreren o nkaitin enye? 
24  Nintasheyie te nkaraki kewan ino iltung'ana linono Israel metaa iltung'ana linono ntarasi; ore iyie, Olaitoriani, niaku Enkai enye. 
25  Ore taata, Ee Olaitoriani Enkai, ntisipa ntarasi ilo rorei liroro iyie oipirta osinka lino neipirta enkaji enye, nias anaa eniroro; 
26  naa kerupi enkarna ino ntarasi, eji, ‘Olaitoriani loo lororani ninye Enkai oo Siraeli,’ ore enkaji o sinka lino Daudi neitubulari te dukuya iyie. 
27  Amu iyie, ee Olaitoriani loo lororani, Enkai e Israel, naitayio ena bolunoto aitodol osinka lino, ijo, ‘Kaashetaki iyie enkaji;’ neaku etagolo osinka lino oshoke pee kiomon iyie ena omono. 
28  Ore taata, iyie Olaitoriani Enkai, iyie Enkai, nesipa irorei linono, nisiligie ena toki sidai osinka lino; 
29  ore naa taata tishipayu iyie pee imayian enkaji osinka lino, pee etum ashomo dukuya ntarasi te dukuya iyie; amu ore iyie, ee Olaitoriani Enkai, niroro, naa te mayianata ino emayiani enkaji o sinka lino ntarasi.”

